# flow 1 login to punjab tracking dashboard
1. go to https://dashboard-tracking.punjab.gov.pk/
2. goto //*[@id="user_username"] add username sed.chk
3. goto //*[@id="user_password"] add password chakwal@951
4. extract the text from /html/body/div/div/div/div/div/div/form/div[3]/div/div/span
4.1 text will be What is 7 + 3? etc (there will be two numbers always)
4.2 extract the two numbers and calculate the sum
4.3 goto //*[@id="captcha"] add the sum calculated in step 4.2
5. click on /html/body/div/div/div/div/div/div/form/button
6. wait for page to load
7. stop there


# flow 2 after login goto tracking page
1. after login goto https://dashboard-tracking.punjab.gov.pk/user_wise_larva_report
2. from this dropdown click //*[@id="district_id"] select Chakwal wait for 4 sec
3. from this dropdown select //*[@id="date_range"] select Today wait for 4 sec
4. click on //*[@id="link-dormant"] 
5. wait for 10 sec
6. click on //*[@id="btn-export-csv"]
7. we will get csv file downloaded
8 save this csv
9. stop there